Chełsty  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Lidzbark, within Działdowo County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north of Lidzbark,  west of Działdowo, and  south-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
